column5: Finally got my line through some ice and also brought in some perch. Not big ones but still had fun.
Awesome dude Looking forward to wetting some hardware too    soon Leechman
looks like fun! I got out today for the first time today...felt good to be on the ice!
sounds like a few of us got out there today for the first time. A few perch is better than sitting at home (or even worse...shoveling snow!)
Awesome, WTG!!! Also got out on the ice today  Already dreamin' about the next time I'm out.....beats cleanin' house & doing laundry hahaha!!!!
Good stuff. Good to get out there eh?
I got out too  sure is great to get the icefishing season under way
